size=3><FONT face=宋体>【例<SPAN lang=EN-US>2</SPAN>】<SPAN lang=EN-US>A 
</SPAN>公司、<SPAN lang=EN-US>B </SPAN>公司、<SPAN lang=EN-US>C </SPAN>公司对<SPAN 
lang=EN-US>D </SPAN>公司的表决权比例分别为<SPAN lang=EN-US>50%</SPAN>、<SPAN 
