size=3><FONT face=宋体>【例<SPAN lang=EN-US>3</SPAN>】假设<SPAN lang=EN-US>A 
</SPAN>公司、<SPAN lang=EN-US>B </SPAN>公司、<SPAN lang=EN-US>C </SPAN>公司、<SPAN 
